# Claude Code: track project config, ignore per-machine / session state.
# Use **/ prefix so patterns apply to any subproject's .claude/ directory.
**/.claude/settings.local.json
**/.claude/worktrees/
**/.claude/projects/
**/.claude/cache/
**/.claude/file-history/
**/.claude/backups/
**/.claude/paste-cache/
**/.claude/agent-memory/
**/.claude/history.jsonl
**/.claude/mcp-needs-auth-cache.json
# Rules under .claude/rules/ are auto-copied from ~/.claude/ by SessionStart
# hooks. Ignore all, allowlist project-specific ones committed directly.
**/.claude/rules/*
!**/.claude/rules/testing.md
!**/.claude/rules/context7.md

# Unsloth compiled cache — regenerated every training run
**/unsloth_compiled_cache/

